    <item>
      <title>法国的贝鲁（Bayrou）规定，将退休年龄恢复到62</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/france-s-bayrou-rules-out-bringing-retirement-age-back-to-62</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁（Francois Bayrou）以养老金制度的财务状况为由，将法国退休年龄带到62岁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/france-s-bayrou-rules-out-bringing-retirement-age-back-to-62</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 14:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
